      <p>Have you been using the same CUCKOO Water Purifier for a long time? 5 years? 6 years? 7 years?</p>
      
      <p>While CUCKOO products are known for their durability and regular maintenance service, water purification technology is constantly evolving. You might be wondering, what should you do with your old machine that is out of contract or was purchased outright (cash)?</p>
      
      <p>Don't let your old machine linger; replace it with a brand new one! Now, you have the opportunity to upgrade your healthy living lifestyle with the latest CUCKOO Water Purifier models through the <strong>CUCKOO GOOOD TRADE-IN Plan!</strong> This program is specially designed for loyal CUCKOO customers to get the newest Cuckoo purifiers at a much more affordable price.</p>
      
      <h2>1. Who is Eligible for the CUCKOO GOOOD TRADE-IN?</h2>
      
      <p>This <strong>Trade-In</strong> program is exclusive to <strong>existing CUCKOO customers</strong> who have previously registered a Cuckoo product. The main eligibility is based on the current status of your CUCKOO Water or Air Purifier contract:</p>
      
      <ul>
      <li><strong>Completed Rental Contract:</strong> Customers who have finished their rent-to-own contract without any outstanding payments.</li>
      
      <li><strong>Outright Purchase:</strong> Customers who bought the product outright (cash) some time ago.</li>
      
      <li><strong>Short Remaining Contract:</strong> Some promotions allow customers with a remaining contract balance of around six (6) months or less to <strong>trade-in</strong>, provided they have no arrears and a good payment record.</li>
      </ul>
      
      <blockquote>
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> The <strong>Trade-In</strong> program only allows the exchange of products within the same category (Water Purifier for a new Water Purifier).</p>
      </blockquote>
      
      <h2>2. What are the Main Benefits of the CUCKOO GOOOD TRADE-IN Plan?</h2>
      
      <p>Subscribing to this <strong>Trade-In</strong> program offers several unique advantages, among them:</p>
      
      <table>
              <thead>
                  <tr>
                      <th>Main Benefit</th>
                      <th>Benefit Description</th>
                  </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                  <tr>
                      <td data-label="Main Benefit">Lower Monthly Payments</td>
                      <td data-label="Benefit Description">Starting from as low as RM59/month, you can enjoy a much cheaper monthly installment price for a new model compared to regular new customers. This allows you to save hundreds of Ringgit throughout the contract period.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                      <td data-label="Main Benefit">Replace with a Newer Purifier</td>
                      <td data-label="Benefit Description">Your current purifier may be over 5 years old, out of warranty, discoloured, inefficient, and utilizing older technology. It's time to *upgrade* to newer, more efficient technology.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                      <td data-label="Main Benefit">Service & Warranty</td>
                      <td data-label="Benefit Description">You will start a new contract that includes FREE periodic service (CCS) and filter replacement for the new contract period (up to 5 years). You don't have to worry about expensive annual service costs for the old machine.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                      <td data-label="Main Benefit">Freshen Up Your Kitchen</td>
                      <td data-label="Benefit Description">Exchange your old machine, which might be worn out or yellowish, for a new model that is more modern, stylish, and neat.</td>
                  </tr>
              </tbody>
          </table>
      
