      <h2>4. Simple Steps to Trade In Your Cuckoo Purifier</h2>
      
      <p>The process to <em>upgrade</em> your CUCKOO Purifier is very simple and straightforward:</p>
      
      <ol start="1">
      <li><strong>Check Eligibility:</strong> Contact your CUCKOO sales representative (Fadhil Cuckoo or Nurul 'Izzah Cuckoo) and provide your old machine's contract information (or outright purchase details) to confirm your <strong>Trade-In</strong> eligibility.</li>
      
      <li><strong>Choose the New Model:</strong> Select the latest CUCKOO Water Purifier model you want (Example: King Top 2).</li>
      
      <li><strong>Registration Management:</strong> The sales representative will handle all registration and application for the new contract at the discounted <strong>Trade-In</strong> price.</li>
      
      <li><strong>Installation &amp; Handover:</strong> The CUCKOO team will arrive to install your new machine. Your old CUCKOO machine will be handed over to CUCKOO on the same installation day.</li>
      
      <li><strong>Enjoy the New Purifier:</strong> You can now enjoy healthy <strong>Mineral &amp; Mild-Alkaline Water</strong> with a new machine, lower monthly payments, and a 5-year service warranty!</li>
      </ol>
      
